Now, I have NEVER had a rpoblem with and uploaders that were VIPs here. So I would believe Tauseef...

BUT to be safe, you can always create a test machine under VMWARE folks. Run proggies under that then wipe it clean when done. Wash, rinse...repeat!!! lol

I use keygens under it, generate 20 or so keys..then copy and paste them into a txt file and keep that. Then you can save your keygen into a compressed, encrypted file for later use if needed.

I do this even if it comes from a VIP simply because no one is perfect...viruses are tricky and things happen. 

An ounce of prevention is worth more than a pound of cure. lol

Heh guys but I suggest you to use Sanboxie to deal up with keygens
